<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Portofolio</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="topbar">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="#home">Portofolio Saya</a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#about">Tentang</a>
        <a href="#skills">Keahlian</a>
        <a href="#projects">Proyek</a>
        <a href="#contact">Kontak</a>
      </nav>
      <button id="themeToggle" class="theme-toggle">Mode Gelap</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <section id="home" class="hero">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="eyebrow">Halo, saya</p>
        <h1 id="heroName">Nama Anda</h1>
        <p id="heroSubtitle">Saya developer web yang suka menciptakan pengalaman digital cepat dan menarik.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="button" href="https://github.com/your-username" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lihat GitHub</a>
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="assets/cv.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Unduh CV</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-image">
        <div class="hero-card">Portofolio</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="section-card">
      <h2>Tentang Saya</h2>
      <p id="aboutText">Saya seorang profesional teknologi yang mengembangkan website modern dengan tampilan bersih dan performa optimal.</p>
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-item"><strong>10+</strong><span>Proyek</span></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><strong>5</strong><span>Skill Utama</span></div>
        <div class="stat-item"><strong>3</strong><span>Tahun Pengalaman</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="skills" class="section-card">
      <h2>Keahlian</h2>
      <div class="chips" id="skillsList"></div>
    </section>

    <section id="projects" class="section-card">
      <h2>Proyek Terbaru</h2>
      <div class="project-grid" id="projectGrid"></div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="section-card contact-card">
      <h2>Hubungi Saya</h2>
      <p id="contactText">Jika Anda memiliki gagasan atau ingin bekerja sama, silakan kirim pesan.</p>
      <a class="button" href="mailto:email@domain.com">Kirim Email</a>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p>© 2026 Portofolio. Isi konten dapat diubah kapan saja pada <code>script.js</code>.</p>
  </footer>

  <div id="editModal" class="modal hidden">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <h3>Edit Konten Portofolio</h3>
      <p>Anda dapat mengubah judul, deskripsi, daftar skill, dan proyek di file <code>script.js</code>. Buka file tersebut untuk menyesuaikan konten dengan profil Anda.</p>
      <button class="button" id="closeModal">Tutup</button>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
